{"word":"ὅδε","slug":"ὅδε","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ὅδε, ἥδε, τόδε</el></b> [combination of <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ὁ\">ὁ</a>, ἡ, τό, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:δέ\">δέ</a></el>] <b><a href='B:490 10:39'>Lk 10:39</a>; <a href='B:510 21:11'>Ac 21:11</a>; <a href='B:730 2:1'>Rv 2:1</a></b> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ freq.\">freq.</a> in Rv<b>.</b> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:εἰς\">εἰς</a> τήνδε τὴν πόλιν</el> to such and such a place/city (= ‘a city we have in mind’) <b><a href='B:660 4:13'>Js 4:13</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ὄγκος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ὁδεύω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}